title: I'm Never Eating Bologna Again.... (108 Slices Challenge)
author: Matt Stonie
description:
Good Video? Smash that Like Button!

How many times must I eat Bologna!!!!
This is my 4th attempt at making a decent Bologna video... All other times something happened that ruin the take. Let's hope that today, I am one with the Bologna.

ENJOY!!!
